A state of activating and testing the energy within you
=========================================
Energy is such a stuff none can create and non can destroy it,since it is the existence/base of the existence of each and every things in this universe. It is one of the co-existence
of nature. It Just like time and space that non can create/destroy them. The time and space support the energy for their streaming and streaming of energy is the core center
