Every one can use the energy in proper/non proper ways but they can't touch its nature of streaming. Whatever you can do with energy, it will be always in state of streaming, it
exists in state of being forever.

You can make it in the state of abstract form or you can activate the abstract form of energy but which state of energy you make abstract and which state of energy you activate that
completely depends up the state of energy within you nothing else.

***Two symmetrical/similar state of energy can interact(heal/diminish) with each others***

