-If you need energy then you should awareness about the space/place form where you can collect the energy.
..so on

Whatever you do on this earth you can define it in infinite ways but the there is only one central reason/purpose behind it is trying to stabilize(collecting energy for use)
yourself.
Who is it that need stabilization and why it never stabilize in their entire life of journey?
It is mind/mask/non realistic stuff who try to stabilize itself on this world and its every activity for its stabilization. The things not exists they never be stabilize completely but it seems to be
stabilize during journey.
In other words/better ways you can say the mind(a very poor state of energy) exists in very poor state of energy and a poor state of energy always are in state of its stabilization.  It is
the nature of energy.

The center of energy exists within you for your stability or transformation. You /your mind search energy to external world in each and every moment of journey but it never
