***within is only space from where you can change the state of life***

Testing of energy within
---------------------------------
Whatever you do in this world the purpose behind these activity is nothing but stabilizing yourself. Many times in your life you seems to be gating energy from external source of
energy ie feeling happy and many times you realize you burn the energy by touching the external source of energy.

Many times you seems to be stabilize your life and many time you seems to be destabilize your life by exchanging energy from external source of energy. But externally whatever
energy you trying to exchange is dust of energy, it never affect you life from inside.

The effect of external source of energy always swimming on your surface of mind/surface of heart. The mask of life only searching energy to external source ie towards the mask of
wold.
The external source of energy(dust/mask of energy) is for testing the energy within, it is not for fertilization/activating of energy within. When you feel pain/stress then
it saying energy within is insufficient and when you feel light then it saying the energy within you are in sufficient state for movement of further sate of life.

***External source of energy is just for testing of energy within you,it never useful for activation/fertilization of energy within***
***Max to Max external source of energy spark you***

